    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this absolute gem! It\u2019s been my pride and joy, and honestly, it looks and feels just like it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve totally babied this car\u2014always kept it in the garage and made sure it stayed spotless. It is in truly pristine condition, inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been incredibly well-loved and is ready for its next adventure without a single worry, this is the one! I'm so excited for someone else to enjoy it as much as I have. Come take a peek\u2014you're going to love it!",
      "price": 44500.0,
